            <string language="x-mt-fr">Gluconéogenèse</string>

          <description>
            <string language="en">This illustration shows the conversion of non-carbohydrate substances in the liver such as amino acids, fats, lactate and pyruvate to glucose through gluconeogenesis.</string>
          </description>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese Abbildung zeigt die Konvertierung der 
Nichtkohlenhydrat Substanzen in der Leber wie Aminosäuren, Fetten, 
Laktat und Pyruvat zur Glukose durch Glukoneogenesis.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette illustration montre la conversion des 
substances de non-hydrate de carbone dans le foie tel que des acides 
aminés, des graisses, le lactate et le pyruvate en glucose par la 
gluconéogenèse.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta ilustração mostra a conversão de 
substâncias do non-hidrato de carbono no fígado tal como 
aminos-ácido, gorduras, lactate e pyruvate ao glucose com o 
gluconeogenesis.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questa illustrazione mostra la conversione delle 
sostanze del non-carboidrato nel fegato quali gli amminoacidi, i 
grassi, il lattato ed il piruvato a glucosio con la gluconeogenesi.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτή η απεικόνιση εμφανίζει τη μετατροπή των ουσιών 
μη-υδατανθράκων στο συκώτι όπως τα αμινοξέα, τα λίπη, lactate 
και pyruvate στη γλυκόζη μέσω gluconeogenesis.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esta ilustración muestra la conversión de las 
sustancias del no-carbohidrato en el hígado tal como aminoácidos, 
grasas, lactato y pyruvate a la glucosa con gluconeogénesis.</string>
          </description>
